'''洛迪高·荷西·利馬·杜斯山度士'''（Rodrigo José Lima dos Santos，{{bd|1983年|5月11日}}），簡稱'''利馬'''，巴西職業足球員，司職前鋒。曾效力[[阿聯酋阿拉伯海灣聯賽|阿聯酋阿拉伯海灣聯賽]]球會[[阿爾阿里足球會|阿爾阿里]]。

==球會生涯==

===早年===
出生於巴西[[蒙特阿萊格雷_(帕拉州)|蒙特阿萊格雷]]的利馬曾效力九支本土球會，但都效力不長。其中在2008年[[巴甲|巴甲]]，他未能為所屬的{{fc|山度士}}取得入球，該會亦只能以第15名完成聯賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://football.hkjc.com/football/statistics/chinese/centre/TeamResult.aspx?ci=zh-HK&goal_type=0&ha=0&hdc=-2&hf=0&hha=-1&idol=1&isFG=1&league_no=1113&league_type=3&nf=0&player_pos=0&s_type=0&season_id=570&ss=1&team_no=576|title=球隊賽績 - 聯賽 - 足球資訊 - 香港賽馬會|publisher=|accessdate=16 May 2015|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006030835/http://football.hkjc.com/football/statistics/chinese/centre/TeamResult.aspx?ci=zh-HK&goal_type=0&ha=0&hdc=-2&hf=0&hha=-1&idol=1&isFG=1&league_no=1113&league_type=3&nf=0&player_pos=0&s_type=0&season_id=570&ss=1&team_no=576|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年夏天，在與烏克蘭球會[[米達列斯|米達列斯]]簽約失敗後<ref>[http://www.itasportpress.it/?action=read&idnotizia=10455 Metalist, acquistato l'attaccante brasiliano Lima (Metalist, signs Brazilian forward Lima)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itasportpress.it/?action=read&idnotizia=10455 |date=20190121232507 }}; Ita Sport Press, 21 July 2009 (Italian)</ref>，利馬轉會至葡萄牙的[[比蘭倫斯|比蘭倫斯]]，雖然為球會取得不少入球，但球會仍要在2009/10球季降班。

===布拉加===
之後，利馬加盟該國的另一支球會{{scl|布拉加}}，簽約三年。2010年8月24日，他在對[[西維爾|西維爾]]的[[歐聯|歐聯]]第三圈賽事次回合以後備身份大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，助球隊以4:3擊敗對手，並以總比數5:3晉級<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/aug/24/Braga-sevilla-champions-league|title=Braga beat Sevilla in Spain to reach Champions League group stage|publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=25 August 2010|accessdate=26 August 2010|archive-date=2010-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100827181430/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/aug/24/braga-sevilla-champions-league|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

利馬在2011/12球季取得26個入球，當中包括20個聯賽入球，助布拉加取得季軍，並取得2012/13球季歐聯參賽資格。利馬接連在作客3:0擊敗[[基維辛迪|基維辛迪]]取得三球、主場5:2擊敗[[費利拿|費利拿]]及3:0擊敗{{fc|塞圖巴爾}}時梅開二度，亦在主場1:1逼和[[賓菲加|賓菲加]]一戰為球隊射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]扳平<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-liga-sagres-news/28950-Braga-1-1-benfica|title=Braga 1–1 Benfica|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=6 November 2011|accessdate=14 May 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331052442/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-liga-sagres-news/28950-braga-1-1-benfica|archivedate=2014年3月31日}}</ref>，他亦在作客火龍球場對應屆冠軍{{fc|波圖}}時梅開二度，但仍以2:3落敗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-liga-sagres-news/29933-unstoppable-hulk-puts-porto-back-on-top|title=Unstoppable Hulk puts Porto back on top|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=27 November 2011|accessdate=14 May 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125161207/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-liga-sagres-news/29933-unstoppable-hulk-puts-porto-back-on-top|archivedate=2012年1月25日}}</ref>。

===賓菲加===
2012年8月31日，在夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]的最後一日，利馬於賓菲加簽約四年，與[[米高·蘇沙·達施華|米高]]換隊<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=1854507.html#benfica+Bragas+lima|title=Benfica buy Braga's Lima|publisher=UEFA.com|date=1 September 2012|accessdate=19 September 2012|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003233832/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=1854507.html#benfica+Bragas+lima|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dn.pt/desporto/benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=2746101|title=Lima no Benfica e Michel no Braga|trans_title=Lima in Benfica and Michel in Braga|publisher=[[Diário_de_Notícias|Diário de Notícias]]|language=pt|date=31 August 2012|accessdate=2 September 2012|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142211/http://www.dn.pt/desporto/benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=2746101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在加盟不久已有不俗的發揮，並搶走[[奧斯卡·卡度素|奧斯卡·卡度素]]的主力射手之位，在其首兩場正式比賽中亦取得入球，其中在作客2:2戰和{{fc|科英布拉大學}}取得一個入球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/36693-benfica-drop-two-points-in-coimbra|title=Benfica drop two points in Coimbra|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=23 September 2012|accessdate=23 October 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522023428/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/36693-benfica-drop-two-points-in-coimbra|archivedate=2013年5月22日}}</ref>，以及作客[[費利拿|費利拿]]梅開二度贏2:1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/36773-lima-brace-gives-benfica-victory|title=Lima brace gives Benfica victory|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=28 September 2012|accessdate=23 October 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130222004147/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/36773-lima-brace-gives-benfica-victory|archivedate=2013年2月22日}}</ref>，歐聯分組賽對[[莫斯科斯巴達|莫斯科斯巴達]]為球隊破蛋，仍以1:2落敗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2013/matches/round=2000347/match=2009532/postmatch/report/index.html#spartak+register+first+points|title=Spartak profit from Jardel misfortune|publisher=UEFA.com|date=23 October 2012|accessdate=23 October 2012|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806165119/http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2013/matches/round=2000347/match=2009532/postmatch/report/index.html#spartak+register+first+points|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在全季，他以30個入球成為聯賽神射手<ref>{{cite news|title=Lima e a marca dos trinta golos|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=821222|accessdate=21 September 2014|work=Record|date=12 May 2013|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714213840/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=821222|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2013年1月26日，利馬攻入其第八個聯賽入球，助球隊以2:1擊敗其舊會布拉加<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-Braga-news/38996-Braga-v-benfica-live-text-updates|title=Braga 1–2 Benfica|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=26 January 2013|accessdate=7 February 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522222636/http://portugoal.net/index.php/more-braga-news/38996-braga-v-benfica-live-text-updates|archivedate=2013年5月22日}}</ref>。3月30日，他首次在葡超大演帽子戲法，助球隊6:1大勝[[里奧艾維|里奧艾維]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=392275|title=Benfica goleia Rio Ave (6–1)|trans_title=Benfica routs Rio Ave (6–1)|publisher=[[A_Bola|A Bola]]|language=pt|date=30 March 2013|accessdate=1 April 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003153/http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=392275|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2013/14球季，利馬在2014年4月20日以2:0擊敗[[奧漢倫斯|奧漢倫斯]]一戰包辦全部兩個入球，並在各項賽事攻入二十個入球，令球會奪得他們第33次聯賽冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/44882-benfica-champions-2013-14|title=Lima double clinches title for Benfica|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=20 April 2014|accessdate=22 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425020022/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-benfica-news/44882-benfica-champions-2013-14|archivedate=2014年4月25日}}</ref>。在之後對[[祖雲達斯|祖雲達斯]]的[[歐霸盃|歐霸盃]]準決賽首回合，在84分鐘取得奠定勝局的入球，助球隊2:1取勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2014/matches/round=2000473/match=2012677/postmatch/report/index.html#lima+puts+benfica+against+juventus|title=Lima puts Benfica on top against Juventus|publisher=UEFA.com|date=24 April 2014|accessdate=24 April 2014|archive-date=2018-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113130810/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2014/matches/round=2000473/match=2012677/postmatch/report/index.html#lima+puts+benfica+against+juventus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的第21個入球，助球會贏得[[三冠王|三冠王]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Lima: “Benfica é um Clube exigente que procura sempre mais”|url=http://www.slbenfica.pt/noticias/detalhedenoticia/tabid/2788/ArticleId/36555/language/pt-PT/Lima-Benfica-e-um-Clube-exigente-que-procura-sempre-mais.aspx|accessdate=21 September 2014|work=SL Benfica.pt|date=21 May 2014|language=pt|archive-date=2014-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140901010652/http://www.slbenfica.pt/noticias/detalhedenoticia/tabid/2788/ArticleId/36555/language/pt-PT/Lima-Benfica-e-um-Clube-exigente-que-procura-sempre-mais.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年9月21日，利馬在對[[摩里倫斯|摩里倫斯]]的聯賽攻入其首個入球，終結至4月21日起持續長達12場的入球荒<ref>{{cite news|title=Benfica-Moreirense, 3-1 (crónica)|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga-benfica-moreirense-cronica-benfica-vence-moreirense/541f11820cf2d28a53792c3a.html|accessdate=21 September 2014|work=Maisfutebol|date=21 September 2014|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006121035/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga-benfica-moreirense-cronica-benfica-vence-moreirense/541f11820cf2d28a53792c3a.html|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lima não marca há 12 jogos|url=http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=501445|accessdate=21 September 2014|work=[[A_Bola|A Bola]]|date=19 September 2014|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725013445/http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=501445|archive-date=2015-07-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月14日，利馬為賓菲加梅開二度，助球隊作客擊敗勁敵{{fc|波圖}}2:0<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ligaportugal.pt/oou/jogo/20142015/primeiraliga/13/6 |title=Porto - Benfica (Jornada 13 Primeira Liga 2014-2015) - Liga Portugal |language=pt |date=14 December 2014 |publisher=[[LPFP|LPFP]] |accessdate=1 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225927/http://www.ligaportugal.pt/oou/jogo/20142015/primeiraliga/13/6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年2月15日，利馬在對塞圖巴爾的聯賽梅開二度，助球隊贏3:0<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ligaportugal.pt/oou/jogo/20142015/1/21/9 |title=Benfica - V. Setúbal (Jornada 21 Liga NOS 2014-2015) |language=pt |date=15 February 2015 |publisher=[[LPFP|LPFP]] |access-date=15 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725013151/http://www.ligaportugal.pt/oou/jogo/20142015/1/21/9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月9日，他在對已篤定降班的[[彭拿費爾|彭拿費爾]]再攻入兩球，助球隊贏4:0<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fourfourtwo.com/my/news/primeira-liga-review-lima-nets-brace-benfica-relegate-penafiel |title=Primeira Liga Review: Lima nets brace as Benfica relegate Penafiel |date=10 May 2015 |publisher=[[FourFour